Corbett 1935: 246. Type species. 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Aleyrodidae" genus="Aleuromarginatus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Aleuromarginatus tephrosiae" order="Hemiptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="96" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tephrosiae">Aleuromarginatus tephrosiae</taxonomicName>
